OBJECTIVE

The goal is to make an application of a Sudoku game, which includes the following parts:

1. The generation of a random resolved board.
2. Render of the board of point 1, where, depending on the difficulty chosen, it shows a greater or lesser number of cells to be completed by the user.
3. Allow the filling and deletion of cells with numbers from 1 to 9, according to the user's choice.
4. Validate the board resolved by the user against the solution generated in point 1.
5. Indicate to the user the result of the validation.
6. Perform game restart at any time.

DESCRIPTION

This project was develop using only HTML, CSS, JavaScript and JQuery.


NOTE

The application is still under development.
